"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9SCHdmNCeYIV4dUCU56eX.png?height=344&width=612)\\n\\nPOAPs continue to be the go-to platform for the minting of digital collectibles of all life experiences. As communities continue to grow and get deeper into POAP, manual distribution has become a daunting task. As POAP users, we understand this and work hard to bring new solutions for everyone to enjoy POAP without unnecessary overhead.\\nPOAPs继续成为纪念我们生活经历的数字藏品的首选平台。随着社区的不断发展和对POAP的深入，手工发行已经成为一项艰巨的任务。作为POAP用户，我们理解这一点，并努力为大家带来新的解决方案，让大家在没有费用的情况下，尽情享受POAP。\\n\\n什么是POAP.delivery？\\nIt is a tool to distribute POAPs by requesting the receiver to go into a website that will allow users to connect their wallet and claim a POAP, given their address qualifies. This is very practical if you, as an issuer, have the whole list of Ethereum addresses that should receive the POAP.\\n这是一个分发POAP的工具，要求接收者进入一个网站，允许用户连接他们的钱包，并在他们的地址符合条件的情况下，申领一个POAP。如果你作为发行人，需要提前收集所有将要领取POAP的以太坊地址列表。\\n\\n\\n1- Create your POAP\\n1-制作poap\\nCreating a POAP is easy, just head to this link and fill out the form. If you have any doubts about what you should include in these fields, please check out our FAQs.\\nSince we are creating a Delivery, make sure you leave the Requested Codes field in 0.\\n创建POAP很简单，只需前往此链接并填写表格（[https://app.poap.xyz/admin/events/new）。如果你对这些字段中应包括的内容有任何疑问，请查看常见问题清单（https://poap.xyz/faqs）。](https://app.poap.xyz/admin/events/new%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%AF%B9%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%AD%97%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%96%91%E9%97%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%95%EF%BC%88https://poap.xyz/faqs%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82)\\n由于我们正在创建一个Delivery，确保你将所要求的代码字段留为0。\\n\\n\\n2- Create the POAP.delivery\\n2-创建POAP.delivery\\nOnce your POAP is created, you will receive an email with your Edit Code. Save this code, it will allow you to make changes to your event from now on. Head down to this link and fill out the form.\\n一旦您的POAP创建完毕，您将收到一封包含编辑代码（ Edit Code）的电子邮件。保存这个代码，它将允许你从现在起对你的活动进行修改。请打开这个链接（[https://app.poap.xyz/admin/deliveries/new），填写下面的表格。](https://app.poap.xyz/admin/deliveries/new%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%AB%E5%86%99%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%82)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wSJY0Iwhm9AqLc8Qsx_j5.png?height=430&width=612)\\n\\nEvent ID: the ID of the event you are creating the POAP for. This is normally a 4-digit number associated to your event. You can find it on your event confirmation email. Edit code: the 6-digit code you received via email when creating the event. Add another event: In deliveries, you can set up more than one event for distribution in the same page. Delivery URL: the path to the page. The URL will result in poap.delivery/{Delivery_URL} so no need to put the <https://poap.delivery/>\\nCard Title: the title that will appear on the card on the poap.delivery homepage.\\nCard Text: the text that will appear on the card on the poap.delivery homepage. Max chars: 200.\\nEvent ID：您为之创建POAP的事件的ID，这通常是一个与您的活动相关的4位数数字，您可以在您的活动确认邮件中找到它。\\nEdit code：您在创建活动时通过电子邮件收到的6位数字的代码（上面有提到）。\\nAdd another event：在deliveries中，你可以在同一个页面中设置多个事件进行分发，一般不需要。\\nDelivery URL：发送POAP页面的路径，该URL将产生一个poap.delivery/{Delivery_URL}的路径，所以不需要把在前面增加https://poap.delivery/的网址开头；\\nCard Title：将出现在poap.delivery主页上的卡片的标题。\\nCard Text：将出现在poap.delivery主页的卡片上的文本。最大字符数：200。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BoUSG4x2yDACeHq3GmaIk.png?height=430&width=612)\\n\\n在Delivery页面，也有下列内容需要填写： Page Title: the title that will appear on the poap.delivery page of your event. Page Text: the text that will appear on the poap.delivery page of your event. Max chars: 200. Metadata Title: the title that will appear when you share the poap.delivery in social media. Metadata Description: the description that will appear when you share the poap.delivery in social media. \\n\\nPage Title：将出现在您的活动的poap.delivery页面上的标题。 Page Text：将出现在你的活动的poap.delivery页面上的文本。最大字符数：200。 Metadata Title: 当你在社交媒体上分享poap.delivery时出现的标题。 Metadata Description：当你在社交媒体上分享poap.delivery时将会出现的描述。 \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/--rdPwLqki2zPvDqS6wrr.png?height=290&width=612)\\n\\nImage URL: the URL where your image is hosted. You can look for your event in the event panel and right-click the image of your POAP. Select “Copy Image address” and paste it here. Page Title Image: you can leave this blank。\\n\\nImage URL：您的图像所在的URL。您可以在事件面板（[https://app.poap.xyz/admin/events）](https://app.poap.xyz/admin/events%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E6%82%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%8D%95%E5%87%BB%E6%82%A8%E7%9A%84POAP%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E3%80%82%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9) [ 中寻找您的事件，并右键单击您的POAP图像。选择](https://app.poap.xyz/admin/events%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E6%82%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%8D%95%E5%87%BB%E6%82%A8%E7%9A%84POAP%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E3%80%82%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9) \\\"复制图像地址 \\\"并将其粘贴在这里。 Page Title Image：页面标题图像，你可以不填。\\n\\nAddresses: Input the Ethereum addresses (or ENS) of receivers. Keep in mind that you can add more addresses in the future, but you cannot delete any. The format for the Ethereum addresses should be the following:\\nAddresses: 地址，输入接收者的以太坊地址（或ENS）。请记住，你可以在未来添加更多的地址，但你不能删除任何地址。以太坊地址的格式应该是这样的。\\n0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000002 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000003\\n(Addresses should only be separated by newlines)\\n(地址只能用换行符分开)\\nWhen you are done, click the Create delivery button to submit your delivery request. You will receive a confirmation email once this request has been received by us.\\n\\nDelivery approvals take some time. As soon as your delivery is approved by the POAP team, you will receive an email confirmation. Your delivery card should appear on the POAP.delivery homepage after approximately 10 minutes. Should you find any difficulties, do not hesitate in contacting us via our social channels.\\n\\n当你完成后，点击创建delivery按钮，提交你的delivery请求。一旦我们收到这一请求，你将收到一封确认电子邮件。\\n\\ndelivery审批需要一些时间。一旦您的delivery被POAP团队批准，您将收到一封确认邮件。您的delivery卡片应该在大约10分钟后出现在POAP.delivery主页上。如果您发现任何困难，请及时与官方联系。\",\"timestamp\":1640097447,\"title\":\"如何设置 POAP.delivery（英-中）\"},\"digest\":\"KVFjBCmtjylMZ5DObt3gxsifc5Ml02ws3WJx-BUmeTU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA2EaE2a749103C5631D5525D136EC7B956Dd7c85\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"QciNC0a5HmVnbqOUa8uexi3_-7p2UOISLJxmPXMb9e0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"h_x7xbszscTG6RSGpmo8fm2vsl9_XQyF6bOtkbVcxjY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ajZS5a1oYOyQv6dCld_9t6AoZMH0NMQOyyzL72LHFlA7n2JZE8FStkbi1LcYt6rByUZ0NW5O7zTQrfOTez7o4w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x490138678290fdf73ab7fd95e9fdac846ea511ae98aa6f7f6eeff975821fa76275b0650ab276600dc4cb1a6a095cfef63cc674a61c0a1cab304f5e41cd1080621b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"QciNC0a5HmVnbqOUa8uexi3_-7p2UOISLJxmPXMb9e0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"h_x7xbszscTG6RSGpmo8fm2vsl9_XQyF6bOtkbVcxjY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"KVFjBCmtjylMZ5DObt3gxsifc5Ml02ws3WJx-BUmeTU\"}"